A single inline link renders as a [1] marker with a => line after the paragraph.
```
See [the site](https://example.com) for details.
.
See the site[1] for details.
=> https://example.com 1: the site
```

Multiple inline links each get their own marker and => line.
```
See [alpha](https://a.ex) and [beta](https://b.ex) for more.
.
See alpha[1] and beta[2] for more.
=> https://a.ex 1: alpha
=> https://b.ex 2: beta
```

Link numbering restarts in each paragraph.
```
A [first](https://1.ex) link.

A [second](https://2.ex) link.
.
A first[1] link.
=> https://1.ex 1: first

A second[1] link.
=> https://2.ex 1: second
```
